text: Lycée Anna de Noailles is a senior high school in Évian-les-Bains, France. it had 950 students, including 120 adults. 90 of its students were boarding students. ==References== ==External links== * Lycée Anna de Noailles * * La restructuration du lycée Anna de Noailles - Evian Les Bains - CAUE74 (architectural firm) Category:Lycées in Haute-Savoie
